reviewText: There is just something about this flick that I find makes for good entertainment.  The cast is terrific and in their pre-prime days.  The setting in small town USA, and centered around a Demolition Derby business where the main characters find their lives changing, presents great appeal to this middle America film fan!  Well written, well played, decently directed.  One of my favorites.
Rocket shipping!  Great product!  Thank you!
